comment: Ellis (DAL) sets the screen on Frye (ORL) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.

RHH shows Vucevic (ORL) extends his arms and pushes Ellis (DAL) while setting the screen.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Nowitzki (DAL) was overturned and DAL was awarded possession.

Harris (DAL) moves his pivot foot while trying to escape the trap near midcourt.
